WEBVTT

00:11.800 --> 00:15.280
[1997]

00:21.000 --> 00:21.920
Hurry up!

00:22.030 --> 00:23.190
Are you hidden?

00:23.440 --> 00:24.500
Just wait a minute!

00:27.070 --> 00:28.440
What are you doing?

00:32.350 --> 00:33.000
Doing...

00:33.290 --> 00:34.220
Doing homework.

00:34.330 --> 00:35.720
Then can I hide at your house?

00:35.720 --> 00:36.600
Y-Yes.

00:36.960 --> 00:37.670
Really?

00:39.590 --> 00:40.850
You can hide in my room.

00:44.390 --> 00:45.720
I'll take you upstairs.

01:00.740 --> 01:01.180
No,

01:01.360 --> 01:02.960
that spot is too easy to find.

01:10.380 --> 01:11.460
Can I hide there?

01:12.039 --> 01:12.640
Yes.

01:22.340 --> 01:23.030
Hold on!

01:23.430 --> 01:24.480
Don't betray me.

01:24.720 --> 01:25.890
Don't tell anyone!

01:26.630 --> 01:27.320
I won't.

01:37.009 --> 01:39.270
They definitely won't find me this time.

01:41.580 --> 01:44.300
This seems a bit boring.

01:54.720 --> 01:56.190
I'm asking you what you're doing!

01:56.190 --> 01:58.050
Why aren't you saying something?

01:58.110 --> 01:59.539
Always hiding things, sneaking around!

01:59.539 --> 02:00.750
What are you up to?

02:02.200 --> 02:03.560
Say something!

02:03.890 --> 02:05.360
Always wearing that cold expression—

02:05.360 --> 02:07.220
you don't look like a child at all!

02:09.280 --> 02:10.340
What are you doing?

02:10.880 --> 02:13.030
Waiting for your dad to come back
so you can tell on me?

02:13.030 --> 02:13.990
Let me tell you—

02:14.740 --> 02:16.860
your dad doesn't have time
to come back at all!

02:16.860 --> 02:19.190
I cook and wash clothes for you every day!

02:19.300 --> 02:20.340
I take care of you!

02:20.370 --> 02:21.020
And you?

02:21.760 --> 02:23.490
Have you ever even smiled at me?

02:23.900 --> 02:25.100
You still dare to run?

02:25.210 --> 02:26.210
Stop right there!

02:27.020 --> 02:28.110
You little brat!

02:28.410 --> 02:29.530
Say something!

02:30.530 --> 02:31.480
Run!

02:32.800 --> 02:33.550
You two!

02:34.260 --> 02:35.390
Stop right there!

04:06.830 --> 04:12.750
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:13.120 --> 04:15.390
[Episode 7]

04:51.430 --> 04:52.270
Jin!

04:53.920 --> 04:55.390
Jin, are you home?

04:58.520 --> 04:59.159
Zhou Jin.

05:00.160 --> 05:01.480
Jin, get up!

05:01.800 --> 05:02.680
Jin!

05:05.390 --> 05:06.310
Jin!

05:07.470 --> 05:08.550
Jin!

05:09.600 --> 05:11.180
-Get up, Jin!
-Zhou Jin.

05:12.530 --> 05:13.530
Help me turn over.

05:13.760 --> 05:14.150
Jin!

05:14.180 --> 05:14.980
My arm is numb.

05:15.270 --> 05:16.000
Sorry, sorry.

05:16.000 --> 05:16.750
Jin, get up!

05:16.750 --> 05:17.480
I'll do it myself.

05:17.480 --> 05:18.850
Time to get up and pee!

05:19.070 --> 05:20.870
Sorry, I slept too deeply last night.

05:20.870 --> 05:21.330
Jin!

05:21.350 --> 05:22.050
Are you okay?

05:22.050 --> 05:22.570
I'm fine.

05:22.570 --> 05:24.480
Jin, Jin!

05:24.950 --> 05:26.240
I'll go see what he wants.

05:26.240 --> 05:26.920
Get up!

05:28.040 --> 05:29.110
You stretch first.

05:29.540 --> 05:30.460
Jin!

05:34.480 --> 05:36.720
Jin! Jin!

05:36.830 --> 05:38.070
What are you doing?

05:38.070 --> 05:40.040
Stop yelling, Bin!

05:41.430 --> 05:42.630
You're waking me up!

05:42.630 --> 05:44.830
What's going on so early in the morning?

05:45.510 --> 05:46.970
Where's that guy of yours?

05:47.560 --> 05:48.480
What guy?

05:49.720 --> 05:50.680
Jin.

05:51.600 --> 05:53.240
Look at you, getting all grown up.

05:53.240 --> 05:54.190
You've got a boyfriend,

05:54.190 --> 05:55.990
and you didn't even tell us, huh?

05:57.159 --> 05:58.510
He's not my boyfriend.

05:58.560 --> 06:00.040
Oh, cut the act.

06:00.360 --> 06:02.560
I heard everything clearly last night.

06:03.120 --> 06:04.070
M-Mom.

06:04.390 --> 06:06.070
My God, that was so disgusting!

06:06.070 --> 06:07.270
Watch your mouth.

06:08.830 --> 06:09.600
What, are you mad?

06:09.600 --> 06:10.480
So now we can't even talk about it?

06:10.480 --> 06:11.630
I told you—

06:11.630 --> 06:12.890
he's not my boyfriend.

06:15.160 --> 06:15.950
I'm married.

06:19.680 --> 06:20.990
You came fully prepared, huh?

06:20.990 --> 06:22.160
You're messing with me, eh?

06:22.160 --> 06:23.160
I'm not.

06:25.360 --> 06:25.870
Really not messing with me?

06:25.870 --> 06:27.070
Really not.

06:27.870 --> 06:28.800
You're serious?

06:30.160 --> 06:31.160
I'm serious.

06:32.080 --> 06:33.210
I'm really married.

06:34.190 --> 06:35.630
Wait, wait, wait...

06:35.630 --> 06:36.560
Why did you do it?

06:36.750 --> 06:38.270
What do you think you're doing?

06:38.270 --> 06:39.630
What about Jiang Cheng, then?

06:39.630 --> 06:40.790
You've liked him for so many years,

06:40.790 --> 06:41.800
and now you just get married like that?

06:41.800 --> 06:43.000
What the hell is that?

06:44.480 --> 06:45.159
Bin,

06:45.720 --> 06:47.950
I know I was wrong
not to tell you about my marriage.

06:47.950 --> 06:48.920
But can you please stop

06:48.920 --> 06:51.050
mentioning Jiang Cheng in front of me?

06:51.390 --> 06:51.830
No.

06:51.920 --> 06:52.360
No.

06:53.120 --> 06:53.720
Why?

06:53.720 --> 06:54.560
Why can't I mention him?

06:54.560 --> 06:55.390
What makes it off-limits?

06:55.390 --> 06:56.870
Because I want to move on.

07:05.810 --> 07:06.610
What...

07:07.000 --> 07:08.630
Whatever happened
between you and Jiang Cheng,

07:08.630 --> 07:09.690
I don't want to ask.

07:10.030 --> 07:11.690
And I don't want to take sides.

07:12.240 --> 07:12.680
Yes.

07:13.680 --> 07:14.480
I know

07:15.390 --> 07:16.950
people change when they grow up.

07:16.950 --> 07:18.240
But some things can't change,

07:18.240 --> 07:19.560
and they won't change!

07:20.830 --> 07:21.680
Jin,

07:22.310 --> 07:24.040
actually, you don't know this.

07:24.040 --> 07:26.270
But before you had feelings
for Jiang Cheng,

07:26.270 --> 07:27.680
Jiang Cheng told me

07:27.840 --> 07:28.870
that he felt...

07:31.950 --> 07:32.630
Bin!

07:33.690 --> 07:35.870
You're here early in the morning!
What's up?

07:35.870 --> 07:36.750
Uh, Uncle!

07:37.480 --> 07:39.430
My mom told me to bring you a duck.

07:39.850 --> 07:41.390
You can stew it for soup tonight.

07:41.390 --> 07:41.870
Okay, okay.

07:41.870 --> 07:42.870
For tonight's soup,

07:42.870 --> 07:44.860
and you brought it here
so early in the morning?

07:44.860 --> 07:46.320
I-I-I was just passing by.

07:47.040 --> 07:48.560
D-Don't go yet!

07:48.870 --> 07:50.720
The pickled cucumbers I made are ready.

07:50.720 --> 07:51.630
Take them back with you.

07:51.630 --> 07:53.290
Tell your mom
to keep them in a cool place.

07:53.290 --> 07:53.960
No need, Auntie!

07:53.960 --> 07:55.310
It's not convenient since I'm riding.

07:55.310 --> 07:56.310
Maybe some other time.

07:56.310 --> 07:58.110
Then come over for soup tonight.

07:58.750 --> 07:59.320
No thanks.

07:59.320 --> 07:59.880
What?

08:00.630 --> 08:01.830
Are you guys going out

08:01.830 --> 08:02.600
to eat?

08:03.310 --> 08:03.720
Yes.

08:03.720 --> 08:04.560
My...

08:04.560 --> 08:06.360
hot pot restaurant just opened.

08:07.360 --> 08:07.750
Jin,

08:08.190 --> 08:10.560
how about... we hang out tonight?

08:11.630 --> 08:12.120
Go on!

08:12.360 --> 08:13.310
His restaurant is quite good!

08:13.310 --> 08:14.310
I've eaten there!

08:14.510 --> 08:15.520
The flavor's great,

08:15.520 --> 08:16.720
and the chef is great!

08:17.630 --> 08:18.310
Alright then.

08:18.310 --> 08:20.510
We'll go prepare lunch.

08:20.510 --> 08:21.770
Time to prepare lunch.

08:25.000 --> 08:25.680
Come on.

08:26.000 --> 08:27.920
Wei is back too. We can all get together.

08:27.920 --> 08:28.680
Wei is back?

08:29.480 --> 08:30.510
How long is he staying?

08:30.510 --> 08:31.870
Just until the 17th.

08:32.470 --> 08:33.520
His wife is about to give birth.

08:33.520 --> 08:35.980
He came back
to take his parents to Jingzhou.

08:36.080 --> 08:36.600
Okay.

08:37.669 --> 08:38.360
Hansheng,

08:38.510 --> 08:40.390
let's have hot pot tonight.

08:41.120 --> 08:42.450
I'm fine with anything.

08:44.150 --> 08:44.870
Okay then.

08:45.440 --> 08:47.430
Order a half-and-half pot tonight for me.

08:47.430 --> 08:48.960
He can't handle spicy food.

08:59.910 --> 09:00.840
See you tonight!

09:05.100 --> 09:05.900
I'm so pissed.

09:25.210 --> 09:26.740
Do you know how to overtake?

09:27.270 --> 09:28.080
Yeah, Cheng.

09:28.360 --> 09:29.420
Switch lanes then.

09:29.880 --> 09:30.450
Okay.

09:43.030 --> 09:43.890
[Jin is married, you know?
She even brought that man home!]

09:43.890 --> 09:44.760
[Seeing her parents smile like that
made me want to cry!]

09:44.780 --> 09:45.570
[Cheng! Say something!
I'm having dinner with them tonight!]

09:45.570 --> 09:46.370
[What do you think about this? Tell me!]

09:59.150 --> 09:59.870
Get out.

10:00.090 --> 10:01.150
What's wrong, Cheng?

10:01.150 --> 10:01.670
Get out!

10:46.800 --> 10:47.730
Jiang Cheng?

10:48.600 --> 10:50.000
Care to join me for a meal?

10:51.000 --> 10:52.700
Is this how your boss
invites people to eat?

10:52.700 --> 10:53.890
It has nothing to do with Boss He.

10:53.890 --> 10:55.000
I'm the one inviting you.

10:55.000 --> 10:55.600
No thanks.

10:55.610 --> 10:56.490
Move your car.

10:56.520 --> 10:57.720
I've got things to do.

10:59.380 --> 11:01.020
If you refuse,

11:01.050 --> 11:02.650
I'll tell the traffic police

11:02.670 --> 11:04.440
that there's something wrong
with your car.

11:04.440 --> 11:07.040
You think I'd use my own car
to transport goods?

11:07.240 --> 11:08.240
No, you wouldn't.

11:09.590 --> 11:12.550
But that old silver Buick behind us...

11:12.800 --> 11:14.360
Even though I can't see what's inside,

11:14.360 --> 11:15.200
I believe

11:15.240 --> 11:17.000
they're watching us right now.

11:18.870 --> 11:21.400
I just want to keep you here
for one more night.

11:24.670 --> 11:26.730
The traffic cops are coming this way.

11:27.120 --> 11:27.870
Nine.

11:28.550 --> 11:29.240
Eight.

11:29.790 --> 11:30.480
Seven.

11:31.200 --> 11:31.870
Six.

11:32.470 --> 11:33.150
Five.

11:33.720 --> 11:34.480
Four.

11:34.910 --> 11:35.600
Three.

11:36.320 --> 11:37.000
Two.

11:37.550 --> 11:38.030
One.

11:39.550 --> 11:40.240
You two,

11:40.360 --> 11:41.560
what's going on here?

11:44.010 --> 11:45.310
We'll handle this between ourselves.

11:45.310 --> 11:46.110
I'm in a hurry.

11:46.720 --> 11:47.200
And you?

11:48.030 --> 11:48.960
I'm okay with that.

11:48.960 --> 11:49.790
With a girl this pretty,

11:49.790 --> 11:50.410
how could I object?

11:50.410 --> 11:51.520
Then take photos

11:51.870 --> 11:52.870
and handle things up front.

11:52.870 --> 11:53.630
The traffic is all jammed behind you.

11:53.630 --> 11:54.480
-Okay.
-Sure!

12:03.480 --> 12:04.750
Mr. Yan, everything is ready.

12:04.750 --> 12:05.960
One guest is already in the private room.

12:05.960 --> 12:06.680
Okay, okay.

12:06.710 --> 12:07.240
What would you like to eat?

12:07.240 --> 12:07.840
Tofu skin.

12:07.910 --> 12:08.510
Tofu skin.

12:09.390 --> 12:09.750
Beef.

12:12.150 --> 12:12.960
Wei!

12:17.630 --> 12:18.320
Wei!

12:20.640 --> 12:21.790
Not bad, Bin.

12:22.150 --> 12:23.480
You look pretty decent!

12:23.720 --> 12:24.360
You bet!

12:25.240 --> 12:25.840
Wei!

12:26.440 --> 12:26.960
Jin,

12:27.200 --> 12:29.530
why don't you make a formal introduction?

12:29.600 --> 12:30.480
This is Jiang Hansheng,

12:30.480 --> 12:32.240
a professor at Haizhou University
of Political Science and Law.

12:32.240 --> 12:32.740
Nice to meet you.

12:32.740 --> 12:34.090
[Zhan Wei, Section Chief,
Information Department,]

12:33.150 --> 12:33.860
I'm Zhan Wei.

12:33.860 --> 12:34.360
Nice to meet you.

12:34.090 --> 12:35.450
[Binjiang
Provincial Public Security Bureau]

12:34.510 --> 12:36.720
Wei works in the Information Department
at the Provincial Bureau.

12:36.720 --> 12:38.270
Haven't you met him before?

12:39.000 --> 12:42.000
Professor Jiang, you're quite familiar
with the Provincial Bureau?

12:42.000 --> 12:43.030
I haven't been there in a long time.

12:43.030 --> 12:45.490
I was also
just transferred there recently.

12:46.030 --> 12:46.870
Come on, sit.

12:46.970 --> 12:48.120
Let's sit down and chat.

12:48.120 --> 12:49.080
You guys are making it look like

12:49.080 --> 12:50.200
a government work symposium.

12:50.200 --> 12:51.080
Quick, sit.

12:51.080 --> 12:52.810
Right. Let's have a seat first.

12:53.120 --> 12:53.670
Wei.

12:54.930 --> 12:56.250
Look at how you're dressed—

12:56.250 --> 12:57.220
like some senior government official.

12:57.220 --> 12:58.730
Don't you know I'm intimidated?

12:58.730 --> 13:00.060
You're always so fussy.

13:00.370 --> 13:01.900
Wei, I knew you'd wear that.

13:02.630 --> 13:03.480
I'm used to it.

13:04.090 --> 13:04.660
Jin,

13:04.690 --> 13:05.750
how are your parents doing?

13:05.750 --> 13:06.410
Are they well?

13:06.410 --> 13:07.210
They're fine.

13:07.420 --> 13:09.410
I haven't seen them in a long time either.

13:09.410 --> 13:09.910
How about this?

13:09.910 --> 13:11.260
It's rare for me to come back.

13:11.260 --> 13:12.390
Tomorrow, I'll go to

13:12.430 --> 13:13.720
your home and visit them.

13:13.720 --> 13:14.270
Okay.

13:16.550 --> 13:17.410
Is this better?

13:18.350 --> 13:19.480
That's more like it!

13:19.870 --> 13:21.400
When you're here with me...

13:22.270 --> 13:23.270
don't put on airs.

13:29.010 --> 13:29.600
Mr. Yan,

13:29.620 --> 13:31.150
most of the signature dishes
have been served.

13:31.150 --> 13:31.840
Here are the dipping sauces.

13:31.840 --> 13:33.240
Is there anything else you need?

13:33.240 --> 13:34.400
Well, looking good, right?

13:34.400 --> 13:35.550
Bring us some beer.

13:36.170 --> 13:36.770
Two cases.

13:37.320 --> 13:38.820
Two cases? Who can drink all that?

13:38.820 --> 13:39.840
Two pitchers should be enough.

13:39.840 --> 13:40.840
He doesn't drink.

13:41.550 --> 13:43.350
Does he not drink alcohol at all,

13:43.390 --> 13:44.790
or just not drink with us?

13:45.540 --> 13:46.800
I'll be driving later.

13:48.900 --> 13:49.470
Okay.

13:49.690 --> 13:51.290
Then, Jin, you drink with us.

13:51.780 --> 13:53.590
How about some baijiu?

13:54.000 --> 13:54.910
Beer is fine.

13:56.270 --> 13:57.000
Alright then.

13:57.000 --> 13:57.820
Three pitchers of beer.

13:57.820 --> 13:58.750
Coming right up.

14:07.720 --> 14:09.000
The utensils are sterilized
at high temperatures.

14:09.000 --> 14:10.530
Don't worry. Just use them!

14:14.270 --> 14:15.360
What do you think, Jin?

14:15.360 --> 14:17.090
My restaurant is not bad, huh?

14:17.390 --> 14:18.390
It's pretty good.

14:18.510 --> 14:20.840
Finally seeing you do something proper.

14:21.560 --> 14:22.200
Fine.

14:22.680 --> 14:23.440
Now,

14:24.150 --> 14:25.680
she's the one lecturing me.

14:25.890 --> 14:26.840
Back in the day,

14:26.870 --> 14:28.530
I thought we were comrades in arms—

14:28.530 --> 14:30.400
fellow C-students, sticking together.

14:30.400 --> 14:31.600
Who would've known?

14:32.430 --> 14:33.960
You just up and abandoned me

14:33.960 --> 14:35.340
to take the entrance exam for—

14:35.340 --> 14:35.960
what was it—

14:35.960 --> 14:37.200
Jingzhou Police Academy.

14:37.200 --> 14:39.230
Who wanted to be a C-student with you?

14:39.230 --> 14:40.600
When I went to cram school,

14:40.600 --> 14:42.260
didn't I ask you to come along?

14:42.390 --> 14:43.750
You were the one who didn't want to go.

14:43.750 --> 14:45.150
You had to go chasing after
some girl instead.

14:45.150 --> 14:46.610
And now you're blaming me?

14:47.260 --> 14:48.510
Hansheng, you know what?

14:48.510 --> 14:49.600
He was so bad back then,

14:49.600 --> 14:51.000
always teaching me how to lie.

14:51.000 --> 14:52.670
He told his family he was at cram school,

14:52.670 --> 14:53.760
but actually,

14:53.820 --> 14:55.640
he was out playing with some girl.

14:55.640 --> 14:56.520
Right, Wei?

14:56.630 --> 14:57.320
I remember!

14:57.440 --> 14:58.760
I even covered for him.

14:59.560 --> 15:00.980
See? Wei was always tight-lipped.

15:00.980 --> 15:02.270
He's much more reliable than you.

15:02.270 --> 15:03.470
How am I not reliable?

15:03.910 --> 15:05.510
Didn't I take enough blame for you?

15:05.510 --> 15:07.760
How many times did my parents
beat me because of you?

15:07.760 --> 15:08.830
Come on.

15:09.950 --> 15:12.520
Back then, Chuan protected you,

15:12.550 --> 15:13.930
and Cheng covered for you.

15:13.930 --> 15:15.930
When did your dad ever beat you?

15:16.480 --> 15:18.030
Alright. That was years ago.

15:18.030 --> 15:19.270
You're still holding onto it?

15:19.270 --> 15:20.840
Alright, let's eat. It's boiling.

15:20.840 --> 15:21.970
I remember all of it.

15:22.710 --> 15:24.510
That year, my mom grabbed a broom

15:24.640 --> 15:26.300
and chased me
from one end of the street to the other.

15:26.300 --> 15:27.410
My head was already big—

15:27.410 --> 15:28.930
the next day it was even bigger.

15:28.930 --> 15:30.020
My first love

15:30.200 --> 15:31.500
dumped me right after that.

15:31.500 --> 15:32.830
My poor little heart...

15:33.030 --> 15:34.490
Don't even get me started.

15:35.230 --> 15:36.180
It was all her fault.

15:36.180 --> 15:37.040
She let it slip.

15:37.050 --> 15:38.320
What first love?

15:38.320 --> 15:40.320
Weren't they all your "first love"?

15:40.600 --> 15:41.150
Yes.

15:42.920 --> 15:44.380
When it comes to devotion,

15:44.490 --> 15:47.290
I definitely can't
compare to you and Jiang Cheng.

15:53.960 --> 15:56.020
Hurry, call a waitress to clean it up.

15:58.740 --> 16:00.000
I'll go get a waitress.

16:13.450 --> 16:14.240
Cheng,

16:14.650 --> 16:17.110
I-I'm having a meal
with Jin and her husband.

16:17.490 --> 16:18.570
Man, this meal...

16:18.920 --> 16:20.040
I feel so choked up.

16:20.110 --> 16:21.640
Why do I feel so suffocated?

16:24.600 --> 16:25.440
Eat more.

16:28.510 --> 16:30.170
Mr. Jiang, your guest is here.

16:33.320 --> 16:34.080
Mr. Jiang.

16:35.000 --> 16:35.480
Come on,

16:35.870 --> 16:37.270
have a seat, pretty lady.

16:37.750 --> 16:38.440
Thank you.

16:42.390 --> 16:42.810
How is it?

16:42.810 --> 16:44.600
Not bad, the place I picked, right?

16:44.600 --> 16:45.670
Very good.

16:45.670 --> 16:46.800
You have good taste.

16:49.480 --> 16:50.550
Mr. Yan, all cleaned up.

16:50.550 --> 16:51.960
You used to live at No. 23,

16:51.980 --> 16:52.770
didn't you?

16:53.270 --> 16:53.870
Yes.

16:54.630 --> 16:56.690
We moved after I got into high school.

17:00.030 --> 17:01.600
That young master who lived at No. 23.

17:01.600 --> 17:02.810
That's what we used to call him.

17:02.810 --> 17:04.550
Yeah, yeah, that's right.

17:06.310 --> 17:07.750
I heard some other nicknames

17:07.750 --> 17:08.510
too.

17:09.280 --> 17:10.319
Like what?

17:11.589 --> 17:13.790
Just nonsense we said when we were kids.

17:16.920 --> 17:17.650
Tastes good.

17:17.770 --> 17:19.829
I need to take this call. You guys eat.

17:20.680 --> 17:21.940
Talk less and eat more.

17:24.329 --> 17:25.990
I really like eating gongcai.

17:26.589 --> 17:27.550
I'll put some in.

17:31.680 --> 17:33.540
What university are you at again?

17:33.550 --> 17:34.770
Haizhou University
of Political Science and Law.

17:34.770 --> 17:35.640
Right, yes.

17:36.590 --> 17:38.650
You're a university professor, huh?

17:38.720 --> 17:39.400
Jin,

17:39.550 --> 17:41.400
how did you get so lucky to marry someone

17:41.400 --> 17:42.660
way above your league?

17:44.400 --> 17:45.530
It wasn't like that.

17:45.720 --> 17:46.920
I courted Zhou Jin.

17:47.560 --> 17:48.620
Have more vegetables.

17:48.620 --> 17:50.350
Too much meat is hard to digest.

17:54.370 --> 17:54.960
Okay.

18:00.210 --> 18:01.090
One is enough.

18:19.000 --> 18:19.720
Go on.

18:22.960 --> 18:23.400
I

18:23.400 --> 18:25.000
can understand how you feel.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.310
You finally outlasted Lai Zhengtian,

18:28.310 --> 18:30.440
and it's the perfect time
to show your skills.

18:30.440 --> 18:31.350
Yet, the supply channels

18:31.350 --> 18:32.680
got cut off.

18:32.680 --> 18:34.210
Of course, you're anxious.

18:34.480 --> 18:35.340
But, Mr. Jiang,

18:36.600 --> 18:39.730
when all is said and done,
it's Old Scorpion's business.

18:40.310 --> 18:41.030
You,

18:41.160 --> 18:41.830
I,

18:42.750 --> 18:43.790
and even Boss He—

18:43.960 --> 18:46.310
we're all just pawns in it.

18:47.200 --> 18:48.160
We just need to do

18:48.160 --> 18:49.830
our own parts.

18:50.190 --> 18:50.920
Understand?

18:58.350 --> 18:59.160
So, you're saying

18:59.160 --> 19:01.200
I fought my way through hell

19:01.200 --> 19:01.960
just to end up

19:01.960 --> 19:03.310
playing delivery boy?

19:04.550 --> 19:06.110
That's your business.

19:07.000 --> 19:08.730
Why are you bringing this to me?

19:10.500 --> 19:13.160
Because you're not
just an ordinary messenger.

19:19.720 --> 19:20.960
You can't bring yourself to turn it off.

19:20.960 --> 19:21.820
Just answer it.

19:24.440 --> 19:25.370
Excuse me, then.

19:26.310 --> 19:27.200
Can't I listen?

19:31.000 --> 19:31.680
Sure.

19:37.510 --> 19:38.200
Cheng!

19:39.350 --> 19:40.210
Having dinner?

19:41.090 --> 19:42.600
Look who I'm with.

19:46.110 --> 19:47.070
You guys are having dinner?

19:47.070 --> 19:48.200
Yeah, Cheng.

19:48.680 --> 19:49.880
It'd be great if you came over.

19:49.880 --> 19:51.080
Then we'd all be here.

19:51.830 --> 19:52.760
Wait, not quite.

19:53.440 --> 19:54.160
One extra.

19:54.830 --> 19:55.510
Bin.

19:57.680 --> 19:59.160
I've met her once before.

19:59.440 --> 20:01.680
Last time we met, I forgot to

20:01.680 --> 20:03.070
congratulate her on her marriage.

20:03.070 --> 20:04.160
Pass that on for me.

20:05.050 --> 20:05.690
Cheng!

20:05.920 --> 20:06.920
Alright, I gotta go.

20:06.920 --> 20:07.860
I'm having dinner with a beautiful lady.

20:07.860 --> 20:08.770
That's it. Bye.

20:28.440 --> 20:29.530
What are you two staring at?

20:29.530 --> 20:30.720
Why aren't you two eating?

20:30.720 --> 20:31.330
Jin,

20:31.830 --> 20:34.430
come out for a sec.
I need to tell you something.

20:35.400 --> 20:36.030
Jin!

20:40.810 --> 20:41.400
Zhou Jin.

20:42.410 --> 20:44.810
It's about the thing
you asked me last time.

20:47.270 --> 20:48.600
Can we just eat in peace?

20:52.600 --> 20:54.660
Hansheng, I'll step out for a moment.

20:54.990 --> 20:55.870
Ignore him.

21:05.310 --> 21:06.880
Actually, ever since I saw you yesterday,

21:06.880 --> 21:08.410
I've had a question for you.

21:09.590 --> 21:11.450
I think I know what you want to ask.

21:12.310 --> 21:13.400
So,

21:13.420 --> 21:15.820
wasn't being a police officer good enough?

21:16.070 --> 21:18.070
Anything is better than being a cop.

21:20.350 --> 21:21.580
You were really willing

21:21.580 --> 21:23.240
to give up everything you had?

21:23.920 --> 21:25.480
I'm the one who was abandoned.

21:25.480 --> 21:26.720
The one

21:27.000 --> 21:29.060
who gets abandoned doesn't get a say.

21:31.640 --> 21:33.110
Boss He asked me to stop you this time

21:33.110 --> 21:34.640
because he wanted me to ask—

21:34.680 --> 21:35.590
is there any way

21:35.590 --> 21:36.730
for us

21:36.750 --> 21:38.550
to regain Old Scorpion's trust?

21:40.200 --> 21:41.600
Do you know Old Scorpion?

21:42.110 --> 21:42.830
No.

21:43.440 --> 21:44.680
He never shows himself.

21:44.680 --> 21:46.210
He's practically a legend.

21:47.350 --> 21:48.950
It couldn't be you, could it?

21:53.810 --> 21:54.950
Come on, just tell me.

21:54.950 --> 21:56.410
Don't keep me in suspense.

21:59.400 --> 22:01.130
In Old Scorpion's dictionary,

22:01.590 --> 22:03.390
the word "trust" doesn't exist.

22:03.440 --> 22:04.720
If that's the case,

22:04.790 --> 22:06.650
we're completely finished then.

22:07.310 --> 22:09.880
I... wouldn't say that.

22:11.060 --> 22:12.060
Old Scorpion...

22:12.920 --> 22:14.030
likes surprises.

22:14.270 --> 22:15.200
Surprises?

22:16.160 --> 22:17.000
A tribute,

22:17.200 --> 22:18.200
a show of loyalty—

22:18.710 --> 22:20.170
call it whatever you like.

22:20.880 --> 22:21.770
Boss He,

22:21.790 --> 22:22.650
Lai Zhengtian—

22:22.790 --> 22:23.920
they're old news.

22:23.920 --> 22:25.180
But you're different.

22:25.680 --> 22:26.960
You're fresh.

22:27.900 --> 22:28.920
Can you be more specific—

22:28.920 --> 22:30.380
what exactly does he like?

22:30.750 --> 22:32.510
I can tell you...

22:33.240 --> 22:34.240
what he once lost.

22:34.590 --> 22:35.350
What?

22:36.790 --> 22:37.920
Five years ago,

22:39.270 --> 22:40.710
he lost a young man

22:40.740 --> 22:42.690
who meant a great deal to him.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.110
Who?

22:45.960 --> 22:47.440
That's all I know.

22:47.550 --> 22:48.240
Sorry.

22:49.160 --> 22:51.090
I can't help you any more than that.

22:53.070 --> 22:53.750
Cheers.

23:02.610 --> 23:04.270
It's been years since we last met.

23:04.270 --> 23:05.270
And you know what?

23:05.400 --> 23:07.260
I still find you just as annoying.

23:07.770 --> 23:09.900
I couldn't stand you when we were kids.

23:10.510 --> 23:12.240
And I still can't stand you now.

23:12.830 --> 23:15.710
You were basically
Zhou Jin's little shadow back then,

23:15.710 --> 23:17.240
always trailing after her.

23:17.510 --> 23:19.640
She never even gave you the time of day.

23:20.160 --> 23:20.960
And now?

23:21.890 --> 23:23.350
She actually married you.

23:25.350 --> 23:26.750
Let me ask you something.

23:27.070 --> 23:28.310
Why are you with her?

23:30.680 --> 23:32.140
Is it because you like her?

23:33.030 --> 23:33.680
Or...

23:35.720 --> 23:37.780
because you couldn't accept losing?

23:38.110 --> 23:38.960
However

23:39.420 --> 23:40.350
you see me

23:40.910 --> 23:41.840
doesn't matter.

23:43.070 --> 23:44.470
What about Zhou Jin then?

23:46.000 --> 23:47.960
If it weren't for the fact
that her parents are getting old

23:47.960 --> 23:49.490
and she's the only one left,

23:49.530 --> 23:51.660
do you think she would've married you?

23:52.010 --> 23:53.460
You used to live in Zhizi Alley.

23:53.460 --> 23:54.420
You know that.

23:54.590 --> 23:56.570
You know who Zhou Jin

23:56.590 --> 23:59.050
really considered family since childhood.

24:00.030 --> 24:01.590
Sorry, Professor Jiang!

24:01.590 --> 24:03.350
I kept Jin outside for a bit.

24:03.590 --> 24:04.050
Come on.

24:05.830 --> 24:07.030
You're finally back.

24:07.510 --> 24:08.190
Just in time.

24:08.190 --> 24:08.650
Come on.

24:09.880 --> 24:10.880
Professor Jiang,

24:11.200 --> 24:13.270
the young master over at No. 23.

24:14.100 --> 24:14.860
I wish you

24:15.190 --> 24:16.750
a long and happy marriage.

24:17.350 --> 24:18.310
Come on, cheers.

24:18.470 --> 24:19.670
I told you,

24:19.780 --> 24:20.780
he doesn't drink.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.090
It's different.

24:22.200 --> 24:22.790
This is

24:23.270 --> 24:24.590
a toast to you.

24:25.160 --> 24:26.060
He must drink it.

24:26.060 --> 24:26.590
Right?

24:27.550 --> 24:28.590
He has to drive today.

24:28.590 --> 24:29.320
-Come on.
-I…

24:31.950 --> 24:32.670
Thank you.

24:33.080 --> 24:33.740
Bottoms up.

24:36.770 --> 24:37.370
Hansheng.

24:40.560 --> 24:41.960
Alright, that's enough.

24:46.510 --> 24:47.440
The beer is weak.

24:47.840 --> 24:48.640
Waitress,

24:49.000 --> 24:50.200
bring us some baijiu!

24:50.210 --> 24:51.810
Enough. What are you doing?

24:52.030 --> 24:52.750
No more drinking.

24:52.750 --> 24:53.210
Come on!

25:03.400 --> 25:05.460
I'm leaving early tomorrow morning.

25:06.920 --> 25:09.120
You won't drive into me again, will you?

25:10.000 --> 25:11.400
Boss He just told us to follow you

25:11.400 --> 25:13.160
to see where you delivered the goods

25:13.160 --> 25:14.560
and what the new route is.

25:16.790 --> 25:18.200
So...

25:19.560 --> 25:22.360
you're not planning to
follow your boss's orders?

25:29.630 --> 25:30.420
Did some people

25:30.420 --> 25:31.950
follow the delivery truck?

25:36.900 --> 25:37.450
You two,

25:37.660 --> 25:38.860
what's going on here?

25:39.480 --> 25:41.070
We'll handle this between ourselves.

25:41.070 --> 25:41.900
What about you?

25:41.900 --> 25:42.760
I'm okay with that.

25:42.760 --> 25:44.510
With a girl this pretty,
how could I object?

25:44.510 --> 25:45.640
Then take photos

25:46.000 --> 25:46.920
and handle things up front.

25:46.920 --> 25:47.790
The traffic is all jammed behind you.

25:47.790 --> 25:48.590
-Okay.
-Sure.

25:48.640 --> 25:49.840
Thanks for your help.

26:00.530 --> 26:01.140
Sorry.

26:01.720 --> 26:03.680
Do I need to worry about things
on that end?

26:03.680 --> 26:04.680
We're just tailing you,

26:04.680 --> 26:06.340
not trying to steal the goods.

26:09.030 --> 26:10.090
It doesn't matter.

26:10.680 --> 26:12.280
I'm just a messenger anyway.

26:19.920 --> 26:21.200
Today...

26:22.680 --> 26:23.400
thank you.

26:24.480 --> 26:27.010
Thank you for
being willing to tell me so much.

26:36.290 --> 26:37.490
I'll see you off here.

26:38.310 --> 26:39.240
Get some proper rest.

26:39.240 --> 26:40.370
I'll head off first.

26:42.350 --> 26:43.080
Jiang Cheng!

26:47.240 --> 26:48.970
I don't know what you are doing,

26:49.250 --> 26:50.540
but you're too much of a wild card.

26:50.540 --> 26:51.740
He Wu won't like that.

26:54.440 --> 26:55.550
That's too bad.

26:55.830 --> 26:58.030
I'm still counting on him to make money.

27:00.580 --> 27:02.040
Come up and sit for a while?

27:11.280 --> 27:12.210
I drank too much.

27:12.310 --> 27:13.240
Maybe next time.

27:27.440 --> 27:28.830
Take your pitcher.

27:30.350 --> 27:31.920
We have to finish this one.

27:32.240 --> 27:33.440
That earlier toast

27:34.200 --> 27:35.310
was wishing you'd

27:35.630 --> 27:37.180
have a child soon.

27:38.100 --> 27:39.250
This one

27:39.640 --> 27:41.370
is wishing you a Happy New Year!

27:41.860 --> 27:43.030
Happy New Year, and that's it!

27:43.030 --> 27:43.960
Cheers, come on!

27:46.800 --> 27:47.920
He can drink.

27:47.940 --> 27:49.170
Cheers, come on.

27:56.360 --> 27:57.420
Fill it up, come on.

28:00.900 --> 28:03.050
Stop drinking. Enough! Let's go home.

28:03.080 --> 28:05.400
Don't stop him. He can drink!

28:05.810 --> 28:07.270
You didn't see it earlier.

28:07.290 --> 28:09.490
This guy glared at me when you were out.

28:09.640 --> 28:11.440
He glared at me just now.

28:12.070 --> 28:12.720
Bin,

28:12.900 --> 28:14.070
what exactly are you trying to do today?

28:14.070 --> 28:16.000
What could I do, Jin?

28:16.230 --> 28:18.680
I'm just looking out for you.

28:18.700 --> 28:19.460
Enough.

28:19.680 --> 28:20.310
Jin,

28:20.480 --> 28:21.720
take Professor Jiang and go.

28:21.720 --> 28:23.180
That's about it for today.

28:23.270 --> 28:25.070
We'll get together another day.

28:25.710 --> 28:26.590
Bin has had too much to drink.

28:26.590 --> 28:27.700
I'm not drunk!

28:29.110 --> 28:29.910
Zhou Jin,

28:30.580 --> 28:33.130
what kind of nonsense marriage is this?

28:33.160 --> 28:34.750
Just to put your parents' minds at ease,

28:34.750 --> 28:36.460
you married him so casually!

28:36.500 --> 28:37.830
Do you even know him?

28:38.510 --> 28:39.810
Stop pointing your finger at him!

28:39.810 --> 28:41.250
Are you out of your mind, Yan Bin?

28:41.250 --> 28:42.290
Do you know him?

28:42.350 --> 28:44.270
Who are you to talk about him like that?

28:44.270 --> 28:46.170
Listen up, I've been
holding it in for a long time!

28:46.170 --> 28:47.720
You invited us to dinner,

28:47.740 --> 28:48.780
and I brought him.

28:48.830 --> 28:49.830
Did we eat?

28:49.830 --> 28:50.790
Did we drink?

28:50.820 --> 28:52.220
So what are you doing now?

28:53.160 --> 28:54.960
I treat you as a friend, and you?

28:55.490 --> 28:57.400
You've been
making things difficult for him.

28:57.400 --> 29:00.330
You've been
making things difficult for my husband!

29:00.460 --> 29:01.480
Making things difficult for him?

29:01.480 --> 29:02.880
I did it for your own good.

29:03.640 --> 29:04.240
If you really care about me,

29:04.240 --> 29:05.390
you shouldn't behave like this!

29:05.390 --> 29:06.710
First, don't humiliate him!

29:06.710 --> 29:07.470
Second,

29:07.830 --> 29:09.000
please sincerely

29:09.450 --> 29:10.710
give us your blessing.

29:11.070 --> 29:12.620
Give you my blessing?

29:12.810 --> 29:13.950
Give you my blessing?

29:13.950 --> 29:14.820
Let me tell you...

29:14.820 --> 29:16.680
Give you... Give you my blessing?

29:19.750 --> 29:20.640
From now on,

29:20.720 --> 29:21.850
we're good friends.

29:22.070 --> 29:23.670
No one can bully you anymore.

29:30.850 --> 29:35.510
[1997]

29:38.030 --> 29:40.240
She hit you. Why didn't you run?

29:43.680 --> 29:44.720
My dad said that

29:45.200 --> 29:46.270
when someone shows concern for you,

29:46.270 --> 29:47.160
not answering them

29:47.160 --> 29:48.030
is impolite.

29:48.740 --> 29:49.540
She...

29:50.960 --> 29:51.920
is pitiful.

29:52.920 --> 29:54.240
Just like my mom.

29:54.590 --> 29:56.640
You're the pitiful one when she hits you.

29:56.640 --> 29:58.040
You should tell your dad!

30:00.310 --> 30:02.310
Then there'd be no one at home again.

30:04.750 --> 30:06.210
Would you be alone at home?

30:07.200 --> 30:08.660
Are you afraid of the dark?

30:10.840 --> 30:12.170
You can stay at my place.

30:12.590 --> 30:14.050
My dad is a police officer.

30:14.050 --> 30:15.440
He's not afraid of any bad guys.

30:15.440 --> 30:16.500
He can protect you.

30:17.920 --> 30:18.450
Let's go.

30:21.160 --> 30:22.000
I...

30:22.420 --> 30:23.140
No need.

30:27.830 --> 30:28.750
I'm Zhou Jin.

30:29.440 --> 30:30.310
And you?

30:32.310 --> 30:33.240
Jiang Hansheng.

30:33.590 --> 30:34.400
From now on,

30:34.550 --> 30:35.720
we're good friends.

30:36.480 --> 30:37.480
Remember my name.

30:37.960 --> 30:39.560
No one can bully you anymore.

30:40.960 --> 30:42.030
Jiang Hansheng,

30:42.270 --> 30:43.200
trust me.

30:43.750 --> 30:44.280
Let's go!

30:44.480 --> 30:45.540
I'll take you home!

31:06.460 --> 31:07.190
Zhou Jin.

31:10.290 --> 31:11.030
What's wrong?

31:11.030 --> 31:12.830
You can't drive after drinking.

31:13.130 --> 31:14.210
You drank all the alcohol.

31:14.210 --> 31:15.070
I didn't drink.

31:24.750 --> 31:25.950
Are you feeling sick?

31:39.230 --> 31:40.490
Hansheng, we're home.

31:50.990 --> 31:52.590
Hansheng, get out of the car.

31:57.720 --> 31:58.440
Come on.

32:05.790 --> 32:06.590
What's wrong?

32:06.590 --> 32:07.990
Are you not feeling well?

32:43.440 --> 32:44.680
Are you feeling sick?

32:44.680 --> 32:45.610
Is it really bad?

32:46.240 --> 32:47.840
Do you feel like throwing up?

32:54.920 --> 32:55.550
I don't know

32:55.550 --> 32:57.210
what Yan Bin told you tonight.

32:58.630 --> 33:00.090
But that's all in the past.

33:02.000 --> 33:03.930
Do you still have feelings for him?

33:04.200 --> 33:05.270
I don't.

33:07.310 --> 33:09.110
Then do you have feelings for me?

33:15.920 --> 33:17.650
You don't have feelings for me.

33:18.700 --> 33:19.630
You're drunk.

33:22.600 --> 33:23.280
Zhou Jin,

33:25.000 --> 33:26.030
you can't lie.

33:28.030 --> 33:30.160
Can we wait until you sober up tomorrow

33:30.790 --> 33:32.050
and discuss this then?

33:42.590 --> 33:44.200
You still don't have feelings for me.

33:44.200 --> 33:45.790
That's not true.

34:09.630 --> 34:10.590
Are you mad?

34:17.280 --> 34:18.210
Jiang Hansheng.

34:20.449 --> 34:21.980
I like having you by my side.

34:30.440 --> 34:31.370
Jiang Hansheng,

34:31.560 --> 34:32.360
let's go home.

34:39.850 --> 34:43.469
♪ I should never have let you bear this ♪

34:45.400 --> 34:47.000
Do you really want to know me?

34:47.139 --> 34:51.230
♪ I always want to give you
everything I have ♪

34:49.880 --> 34:51.190
What if Yan Bin is right

34:52.469 --> 34:54.469
and I'm not the person you think I am?

34:54.520 --> 34:58.470
♪ If only it could win your heart,
even for a moment ♪

34:56.030 --> 34:57.030
What do you mean?

34:58.890 --> 35:02.220
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

35:03.760 --> 35:06.040
♪ They're so free ♪

35:06.550 --> 35:07.480
Jiang Hansheng!

35:07.630 --> 35:08.190
Zhou Jin.

35:09.410 --> 35:13.540
♪ I never want to see you hang your head ♪

35:10.400 --> 35:11.400
Will you hate me?

35:13.190 --> 35:15.250
Don't be dramatic when you're drunk.

35:16.710 --> 35:17.370
Zhou Jin...

35:17.420 --> 35:20.490
♪ I keep dreaming of
what lies ahead for us ♪

35:19.840 --> 35:20.670
I love you.

35:24.050 --> 35:27.990
♪ If only it could keep us
in love forever ♪

35:28.510 --> 35:31.740
♪ Look at the zebras ♪

35:49.310 --> 35:53.610
[1997]

35:54.190 --> 35:55.120
Jiang Hansheng!

35:55.190 --> 35:55.800
Mentor!

35:56.000 --> 35:56.600
Hansheng.

35:56.630 --> 35:57.070
Jiang Hansheng.

35:57.070 --> 35:57.510
Mentor,

35:57.510 --> 35:58.480
we've searched everywhere on this side!

35:58.480 --> 35:59.590
We can't find the kid.

35:59.590 --> 36:00.960
Then look further away!

36:01.230 --> 36:01.800
Hurry, let's go!

36:01.800 --> 36:03.000
Go search over there!

36:03.190 --> 36:04.190
Jiang Hansheng!

36:04.190 --> 36:05.360
Hansheng!

36:05.480 --> 36:06.800
Jiang Hansheng!

36:07.000 --> 36:08.000
Hansheng!

36:08.110 --> 36:09.110
Hansheng!

36:09.150 --> 36:11.070
Jiang Hansheng!

36:22.320 --> 36:23.440
We've searched everywhere.

36:23.440 --> 36:24.110
Mentor!

36:24.150 --> 36:26.280
Liu, how's the situation on your side?

36:26.320 --> 36:28.280
We've searched everywhere
but didn't find him, Mentor.

36:28.280 --> 36:29.280
Zhou,

36:29.460 --> 36:30.760
we've searched all around here.

36:30.760 --> 36:32.420
Should we search further out?

36:34.710 --> 36:36.190
Has the station sent anyone?

36:36.190 --> 36:37.320
Let them search this area

36:37.320 --> 36:38.510
carefully again!

36:38.920 --> 36:39.550
Mentor,

36:39.590 --> 36:41.720
w-we've already searched carefully.

36:42.250 --> 36:42.730
Well,

36:42.810 --> 36:45.220
where could a little boy like him
possibly go?

36:45.220 --> 36:47.320
Why hasn't the boy's father come back yet?

36:47.320 --> 36:48.720
He said he's almost here!

36:48.960 --> 36:49.760
Let's do this—

36:50.120 --> 36:52.930
let's go check... um... his place again!

36:52.960 --> 36:54.400
Maybe he went back, right?

36:54.400 --> 36:55.190
Okay, let's go.

36:55.190 --> 36:56.790
-Come on, let's go.
-Come on.

37:13.960 --> 37:14.890
Jiang Hansheng.

37:23.510 --> 37:24.510
Jiang Hansheng.

37:29.000 --> 37:30.150
Are you alright?

37:33.270 --> 37:34.960
I miss my mom.

37:37.440 --> 37:39.150
Then why are you hiding here?

37:40.840 --> 37:41.840
My mom...

37:43.550 --> 37:45.510
is lying in a dark place.

38:15.920 --> 38:16.760
Hansheng.

38:21.510 --> 38:23.230
I think I remember something.

38:44.970 --> 38:46.630
You found something already?

38:47.730 --> 38:48.330
Jin.

38:49.400 --> 38:50.480
I'll just tell you,

38:50.480 --> 38:51.580
and you take it as is.

38:51.580 --> 38:52.440
Can you do that?

38:52.530 --> 38:53.460
I'll try my best.

38:53.800 --> 38:55.340
Back during the follow-up manhunt
after the 8/17 Case,

38:55.340 --> 38:56.640
Yao Weihai was the first

38:56.640 --> 38:59.370
to find the hiding place
of some of the criminals.

39:00.110 --> 39:01.490
He made a great contribution—

39:01.490 --> 39:02.930
that was beyond dispute,

39:02.970 --> 39:05.010
and was widely known.

39:05.820 --> 39:08.080
But that's also when the leads went cold.

39:08.460 --> 39:09.810
Don't you suspect that the reason he

39:09.810 --> 39:11.330
found the criminals first

39:11.510 --> 39:14.310
was because someone on the inside
was helping him?

39:14.370 --> 39:15.700
It's not what you think.

39:16.810 --> 39:18.140
There was an informant.

39:18.490 --> 39:19.300
The informant

39:19.330 --> 39:22.060
provided him with
very important intelligence.

39:22.340 --> 39:23.600
Who was the informant?

39:24.010 --> 39:25.200
I wasn't able to find him.

39:25.200 --> 39:26.850
Since informants have to be protected,

39:26.850 --> 39:29.080
records about the person
might have been made confidential

39:29.080 --> 39:30.330
or destroyed.

39:30.730 --> 39:31.860
At least at my level,

39:31.880 --> 39:33.080
I can't find out more.

39:33.440 --> 39:35.230
And it's not appropriate to dig deeper.

39:35.230 --> 39:37.860
After all, Yao Weihai is leading
the task force.

39:37.860 --> 39:39.520
That could create conflicts.

39:42.390 --> 39:44.260
That informant had direct contact

39:44.260 --> 39:45.590
with the criminal gang.

39:47.130 --> 39:48.290
Can I meet him?

39:52.900 --> 39:54.420
That would be very difficult.

39:54.420 --> 39:55.590
Can you help me,

39:55.620 --> 39:56.260
Wei?

39:57.960 --> 39:58.850
Jin,

39:59.280 --> 40:01.120
I can only do my best.

40:01.680 --> 40:02.590
As long as it doesn't

40:02.590 --> 40:04.720
cause any danger or create any threat,

40:05.180 --> 40:06.310
I'll try to help you.

40:06.330 --> 40:08.060
But you still have to remember,

40:08.130 --> 40:09.330
the greater the hope,

40:09.620 --> 40:11.480
the greater the disappointment.

40:13.440 --> 40:14.400
I know.

40:15.630 --> 40:17.430
I'm used to being disappointed.

40:20.080 --> 40:20.640
Okay.

40:21.770 --> 40:22.830
Wait for my update.

41:08.010 --> 41:11.200
♪ Just one more second ♪

41:10.270 --> 41:11.070
You're awake.

41:11.870 --> 41:15.170
♪ When you're feeling low, is there ♪

41:15.320 --> 41:17.440
♪ Someone to hold you? ♪

41:18.050 --> 41:21.370
♪ When you're trapped, don't you ♪

41:21.410 --> 41:23.340
♪ Wan to escape? ♪

41:24.220 --> 41:27.920
♪ I know how strong you are ♪

41:27.030 --> 41:28.890
Do you still remember last night?

41:31.280 --> 41:32.210
Sorry, Zhou Jin.

41:32.880 --> 41:36.070
♪ Just one more second ♪

41:33.590 --> 41:34.360
I think...

41:34.840 --> 41:35.770
I drank too much.

41:36.700 --> 41:39.950
♪ Did you throw away ♪

41:40.330 --> 41:42.380
♪ The expired drinks? ♪

41:42.900 --> 41:46.450
♪ Though it's lost, you keep ♪

41:46.740 --> 41:48.740
♪ Looking for it ♪

41:48.890 --> 41:50.060
Your ears are red.

41:49.770 --> 41:53.400
♪ I know how fragile you are ♪

42:03.370 --> 42:04.250
Let's go back.

42:13.990 --> 42:17.380
[Zhizi Alley]

42:19.920 --> 42:22.580
You still haven't been
to see my brother, right?

42:26.320 --> 42:27.520
The day after tomorrow,

42:27.520 --> 42:28.920
come with me to visit him.

42:29.750 --> 42:30.420
Okay.

42:36.280 --> 42:38.280
Feels like it's going to rain again.

42:55.990 --> 42:56.790
What's wrong?

42:59.510 --> 43:00.110
Nothing.
